As we guessed above,that is not going to be one of our independent variables,which is better to take it out of model.

From the beggining of our first model,autocorrelation values are disturbant.Then,lag variable could take place in the model, which is able to be better for autocorrelation.

#CONCLUSION

Mortgaged sales in Izmir is related to Buying time condition of durable goods ,Interest Rate on Housing and lag variables that is really beneficial to avoid autocorrelation after observing multiple models based on p values and taking out of worse ones.We provided predicted value of April 2021 that is 2489.702 and plot of real and expected ones at last.
